column5: Anyone in the Hamilton area going to the "Fishing for Tyler" event tomorrow who could stop at my home to pick up the auction rod for Vance?  Any help greatly appreciated.  How bout you Vinnimon?
My wife  might be heading down that way I'll ask when she gets in.
Be there in a little while?
Wonderful, thanks Bruce.  See you shortly.
Done deal, good to see you again Bruce, you and all the other participants have a great day tomorrow.  I know for certain you'd have been there for me Vinnimon but it's been looked after.
